examples.en: The enemy has been shelling us all day
Josie was shelling peas in the kitchen.
The army has been shelling the town since yesterday.
As the day drew on, the shelling eased off a bit.
She was quietly shelling French-beans for her dinner.
After the shelling, many people lost the ability to remember.
How long do I have to go on shelling out for the boy's education?
